		Quad: rdf.Quad{

				Object: rdf.Literal{
					LexicalForm: "Gregg Kellogg",

			},

			encoding.SubjectStatementOffsets: cursorio.TextOffsetRange{

=== Test/Eval/#tli01

encodingtest.QuadStatementList{
	{
		Quad: rdf.Quad{
			Triple: rdf.Triple{
				Subject: rdf.IRI("http://example/A"),
				Predicate: rdf.IRI("http://example.com/foo"),
				Object: bnTODO.NewStringBlankNode("b0"),
